description:
I installed it. It showed up in the list of programs installed, but not under the "Show Applic
ations" menu. I used search, but no results for the app. I rebooted. Still no app. I uninstalled it, then reinstalled it. Still no app in "Show Applications" menu. Again, I rebooted. Still no app in Show Applications. I uninstalled it, again. I am not going to say that the experience was a complete waste of time because I found the information in the description useful which made the experience worth the time. So, I'm giving the information three stars.
it's simple but I like it
